      "content": "Focus on sharp, tailored clothing that fits impeccably; a well-pressed suit or professional dress signals discipline and respect for the occasion. Grooming should be understated yet meticulous—think clean hair, neat nails, and subtle, high-quality fragrance. Confidence is key, so practice strong, deliberate body language, maintaining eye contact to project unwavering authority. These subtle details signal that you are serious, competent, and belong at that executive table.",
