      "content": "thanks for that. can u get a bit more specific with the grooming stuff though? especially hair. i have some clients who are asking if certain hairstyles or just natural looks are okay for these high-level meetings, or if they should be aiming for something more \"neat\" or \"polished\" to make sure they don't look too casual or unprofessional.",
